+# Rust Codebase Refactoring Summary
+
+## Problem Statement
+
+The original Rust codebase had a monolithic structure that:
+- Prevented effective library benchmarking
+- Obscured dependency boundaries
+- Made it difficult to maintain and test individual modules in isolation
+- Mixed low-level utilities with high-level application logic
+
+## Solution Implemented
+
+Restructured the entire Rust codebase from a single monolithic crate into a modular workspace with 7 separate crates:
+
+### New Crate Structure
+
+1. **chroma-proto** (NEW)
+   - Protocol buffer definitions
+   - Generated gRPC types
+   - Foundation for all API communication
+
+2. **chroma-types** (Extracted from worker/src/types)
+   - Core domain types (Collections, Segments, Records)
+   - Metadata and operation types
+   - Error definitions
+   - Depends on: chroma-proto
+
+3. **chroma-distance** (Extracted from worker/src/distance)
+   - Distance metric implementations (Euclidean, Cosine, InnerProduct)
+   - SIMD-optimized code (SSE, AVX, NEON)
+   - Standalone benchmarks
+   - Zero dependencies on other Chroma crates
+
+4. **chroma-blockstore** (Extracted from worker/src/blockstore)
+   - Block storage abstractions
+   - Arrow-based and memory-based implementations
+   - Sparse index utilities
+   - Standalone benchmarks
+   - Depends on: chroma-types
+
+5. **chroma-system** (Extracted from worker/src/system)
+   - Actor system framework
+   - Component lifecycle management
+   - Executor and scheduler
+   - Depends on: chroma-types
+
+6. **chroma-index** (Extracted from worker/src/index)
+   - HNSW vector index
+   - Full-text search (Tantivy)
+   - Metadata filtering
+   - Depends on: chroma-types, chroma-blockstore, chroma-distance
+
+7. **worker** (Refactored)
+   - Main application binary
+   - Query and compaction services
+   - Orchestration layer
+   - Depends on: all chroma-* crates
+
+## Changes Made
+
+### Workspace Configuration
+
+**Before:**
+```toml
+[workspace]
+members = ["rust/worker/"]
+```
+
+**After:**
+```toml
+[workspace]
+members = [
+   "rust/chroma-proto",
+   "rust/chroma-types",
+   "rust/chroma-distance",
+   "rust/chroma-blockstore",
+   "rust/chroma-system",
+   "rust/chroma-index",
+   "rust/worker",
+]
+resolver = "2"
+```
+
+### Directory Structure
+
+**Before:**
+```
+rust/
+└── worker/
+    ├── src/
+    │   ├── types/
+    │   ├── distance/
+    │   ├── blockstore/
+    │   ├── system/
+    │   ├── index/
+    │   └── ...
+    └── Cargo.toml
+```
+
+**After:**
+```
+rust/
+├── chroma-proto/
+│   ├── src/lib.rs
+│   ├── build.rs
+│   └── Cargo.toml
+├── chroma-types/
+│   ├── src/
+│   │   ├── lib.rs
+│   │   ├── collection.rs
+│   │   ├── segment.rs
+│   │   ├── metadata.rs
+│   │   ├── errors.rs
+│   │   └── ...
+│   └── Cargo.toml
+├── chroma-distance/
+│   ├── src/
+│   │   ├── lib.rs
+│   │   ├── types.rs
+│   │   ├── distance_sse.rs
+│   │   ├── distance_avx.rs
+│   │   └── distance_neon.rs
+│   ├── benches/
+│   │   └── distance_metrics.rs
+│   └── Cargo.toml
+├── chroma-blockstore/
+│   ├── src/
+│   │   ├── lib.rs
+│   │   ├── arrow/
+│   │   ├── memory/
+│   │   └── ...
+│   ├── benches/
+│   │   └── blockstore_bench.rs
+│   └── Cargo.toml
+├── chroma-system/
+│   ├── src/
+│   │   ├── lib.rs
+│   │   ├── system.rs
+│   │   ├── executor.rs
+│   │   └── ...
+│   └── Cargo.toml
+├── chroma-index/
+│   ├── src/
+│   │   ├── lib.rs
+│   │   ├── hnsw.rs
+│   │   ├── fulltext/
+│   │   └── ...
+│   ├── build.rs
+│   └── Cargo.toml
+├── worker/
+│   ├── src/
+│   │   ├── lib.rs (updated to use crates)
+│   │   ├── server.rs
+│   │   ├── compactor/
+│   │   └── ...
+│   ├── build.rs (simplified)
+│   └── Cargo.toml (updated dependencies)
+├── README.md (NEW)
+└── MODULAR_ARCHITECTURE.md (NEW)
+```
+
+### Code Changes
+
+#### Import Statements
+
+**Before (worker monolith):**
+```rust
+use crate::types::Collection;
+use crate::distance::DistanceFunction;
+use crate::blockstore::BlockfileProvider;
+```
+
+**After (modular):**
+```rust
+use chroma_types::Collection;
+use chroma_distance::DistanceFunction;
+use chroma_blockstore::BlockfileProvider;
+```
+
+#### Module Exports
+
+Each library crate now has a clear public API in `lib.rs`:
+
+**chroma-distance/src/lib.rs:**
+```rust
+pub mod distance_avx;
+pub mod distance_neon;
+pub mod distance_sse;
+pub mod types;
+
+pub use distance_avx::*;
+pub use distance_neon::*;
+pub use distance_sse::*;
+pub use types::*;
+```
+
+#### Proto Generation
+
+**Before (in worker):**
+```rust
+// worker/build.rs
+fn main() {
+    tonic_build::configure()
+        .compile(&proto_paths, &["../../idl/"])?;
+    // Also compile hnswlib bindings
+    cc::Build::new()
+        .file("bindings.cpp")
+        .compile("bindings");
+}
+
+// worker/src/lib.rs
+mod chroma_proto {
+    tonic::include_proto!("chroma");
+}
+```
+
+**After (separated):**
+```rust
+// chroma-proto/build.rs
+fn main() {
+    tonic_build::configure()
+        .compile(&proto_paths, &["../../idl/"])?;
+}
+
+// chroma-index/build.rs
+fn main() {
+    cc::Build::new()
+        .file("bindings.cpp")
+        .compile("bindings");
+}
+
+// worker/src/lib.rs
+pub use chroma_proto;
+```
+
+### Benchmarks
+
+Added dedicated benchmark support to performance-critical crates:
+
